subject: Upcomming Lessons for Val
body:
Val Lesson Plan: Tue Nov 21, 2023 at 06:30 PM

So, last week Val had said something about a couple of songs he was interested in learning.

If he has practiced, then we will explore those some.

Other than that, we will finish up with "You've got a Friend in Me".

After some thought, I think it would be really great to explore "The Weight", to sort out major and minor barre chords for him.

"Take 5" might be a challenging piece to explore. It's up to Val.
